Employee Onboarding Checklist – Kahana

Owner: HR / Operations
Approved By: CEO
Effective Date: March 2026
Source: https://data-room-two.vercel.app/onboarding

1. Purpose
This checklist ensures new team members complete required onboarding steps, including security and compliance requirements. It supports SOC 2 controls for access provisioning, security awareness, and policy acknowledgment.

2. Scope
Applies to all new employees, contractors, and interns joining Kahana.

