4. Security & Compliance (SOC 2 requirements)
| Step | Owner | Done (Y/N) | Notes |
|------|-------|------------|-------|
| Review SOC 2 & Compliance Policies | HR/Security | | Information Security, Access Control, Password, Encryption, Acceptable Use, Code of Conduct, NDA. Planned: formal policy acknowledgment. |
